Tab tables
==========

using TAB tables exlude the possibility of use the tab indented
code styles. Ordinal code styles will be rendered as TAB tables

```text
some text	another column
just txt	simple text
```

	some text	another column ![][logo]
	just text	simple *text* col2

	single column table row1	![][logo]
	single **_column_** table row2

	single column **single** row


[logo]:data:image/png;base64,
